<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Matías García · Casa Woden</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  :root {
    --black:   #0C0B09;
    --dark:    #141210;
    --dark2:   #1C1A16;
    --dark3:   #26231E;
    --gold:    #B89650;
    --gold2:   #D4B46A;
    --cream:   #EDE8DC;
    --cream2:  #C8C0AE;
    --stone:   #6A6050;
    --stone2:  #8A7E6A;
    --white:   #F8F5EF;
  }

  html { font-size: 16px; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════ SLIDES ═══════════════════ */
  .slides {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
  }

  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity .7s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: all;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════ NAV DOTS ═══════════════════ */
  .dots {
    position: fixed;
    right: 28px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--stone);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  .dot.on { background: var(--gold2); transform: scale(1.4); }

  /* ═══════════════════ ARROWS ═══════════════════ */
  .arrows {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 28px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .arr {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    background: rgba(12,11,9,0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    color: var(--stone2);
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .arr:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold2); }

  /* ═══════════════════ SLIDE COUNTER ═══════════════════ */
  .counter {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 40px;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--stone);
    z-index: 100;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  }
  .counter span { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ═══════════════════ SHARED ELEMENTS ═══════════════════ */
  .tag {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .rule {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    display: block;
  }
  .rule.long { width: 100%; }
  .rule.v {
    width: 1px;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 60px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 1 — PORTADA
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s1 {
    background: var(--black);
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  #s1::before {
    content: 'CW';
    position: absolute;
    right: -60px; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(300px, 35vw, 500px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: -20px;
  }
  .s1-inner {
    padding: 0 80px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeUp .9s ease both;
    animation-delay: .2s;
  }
  .s1-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .s1-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 100px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .s1-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold2);
  }
  .s1-title {
    font-size: clamp(11px, 1.5vw, 14px);
    letter-spacing: 5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone2);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .s1-contacts {
    display: flex;
    gap: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .s1-contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .s1-contact-label {
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone);
  }
  .s1-contact-value {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--cream2);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .s1-gold-bar {
    width: 60px; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 2 — QUIÉN SOY
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s2 {
    background: var(--dark);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
  .s2-left {
    background: var(--black);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    animation: fadeLeft .8s ease both;
    animation-delay: .15s;
  }
  .s2-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px;
    animation: fadeRight .8s ease both;
    animation-delay: .3s;
  }
  .s2-headline {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 68px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
    margin: 16px 0 28px;
  }
  .s2-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold2); }
  .s2-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--stone2);
    line-height: 2;
    max-width: 380px;
  }
  .s2-body strong { color: var(--cream2); font-weight: 400; }
  .s2-stat {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .s2-stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .s2-stat-v {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold2);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .s2-stat-l {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone);
  }
  .s2-pillar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 22px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dark3);
  }
  .s2-pillar:last-child { border: none; }
  .s2-pillar-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark3);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .s2-pillar-text {}
  .s2-pillar-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--cream2);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .s2-pillar-desc {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 3 — LO QUE OFREZCO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s3 {
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 72px 80px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .s3-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 44px;
    animation: fadeUp .7s ease both;
    animation-delay: .2s;
  }
  .s3-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background .3s;
  }
  .s3-card:hover { background: var(--dark3); }
  .s3-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
  }
  .s3-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block;
  }
  .s3-card-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .s3-card-desc {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--stone2);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }
  .s3-card-desc strong { color: var(--cream2); font-weight: 400; }
  .s3-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    animation: fadeUp .6s ease both;
  }
  .s3-main-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .s3-main-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold2); }
  .s3-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--stone);
    max-width: 280px;
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 4 — CÓMO TRABAJO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s4 {
    background: var(--dark);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 360px 1fr;
  }
  .s4-left {
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 80px 52px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    animation: fadeLeft .7s ease both;
    animation-delay: .1s;
  }
  .s4-left-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(44px, 5vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 20px 0 28px;
  }
  .s4-left-title em { font-style: italic; }
  .s4-left-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(12,11,9,0.6);
    line-height: 1.8;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  .s4-tag-dark {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(12,11,9,0.5);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .s4-right {
    padding: 80px 60px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    animation: fadeRight .7s ease both;
    animation-delay: .25s;
  }
  .s4-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .s4-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 28px;
    padding: 22px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .s4-step:last-child { border: none; }
  .s4-step-n {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark3);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .s4-step-body {}
  .s4-step-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  .s4-step-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--stone2);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .s4-step-desc strong { color: var(--gold2); font-weight: 400; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 5 — PARA QUIÉN
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s5 {
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 72px 80px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .s5-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
    animation: fadeUp .7s ease both;
    animation-delay: .2s;
  }
  .s5-quote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream2);
    line-height: 1.4;
    padding-left: 28px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .s5-quote em { color: var(--gold2); font-style: normal; }
  .s5-profiles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .s5-profile {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    transition: background .2s;
  }
  .s5-profile:hover { background: var(--dark3); }
  .s5-profile-icon {
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .s5-profile-text {}
  .s5-profile-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--cream2);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .s5-profile-sub {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 6 — DISPONIBILIDAD
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s6 {
    background: var(--dark2);
    padding: 72px 80px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .s6-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 44px;
    animation: fadeUp .7s ease both;
    animation-delay: .2s;
  }
  .s6-block {
    background: var(--black);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    padding: 40px 36px;
  }
  .s6-block.gold-bg {
    background: var(--gold);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .s6-block-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .s6-block-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .s6-block.gold-bg .s6-block-title { color: var(--black); }
  .s6-block-body {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--stone2);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }
  .s6-block.gold-bg .s6-block-body { color: rgba(12,11,9,0.65); }
  .s6-block-body strong { color: var(--cream2); font-weight: 400; }
  .s6-block.gold-bg .s6-block-body strong { color: var(--black); }
  .s6-avail-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(12,11,9,0.1);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(12,11,9,0.6);
  }
  .s6-avail-row:last-child { border: none; }
  .s6-avail-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--black);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 7 — CONTACTO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  #s7 {
    background: var(--black);
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  #s7::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(184,150,80,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .s7-inner {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeUp .8s ease both;
    animation-delay: .1s;
    padding: 40px;
  }
  .s7-main {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 20px 0 40px;
  }
  .s7-main em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold2); }
  .s7-tagline {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone2);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .s7-contacts {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .s7-contact {
    padding: 28px 44px;
    border: 1px solid var(--dark3);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    min-width: 180px;
    transition: background .2s;
  }
  .s7-contact:hover { background: var(--dark2); }
  .s7-contact:not(:last-child) { border-right: none; }
  .s7-contact-icon { font-size: 20px; opacity: 0.6; }
  .s7-contact-label {
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone);
  }
  .s7-contact-value {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--cream2);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .s7-rule {
    width: 1px; height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin: 40px auto;
  }
  .s7-close {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--stone2);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     ANIMATIONS
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeLeft {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeRight {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     RESPONSIVE
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #s2, #s4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; overflow-y: auto; }
    .s2-left, .s2-right, .s4-left, .s4-right { padding: 48px 36px; }
    #s3, #s5, #s6 { padding: 48px 32px; overflow-y: auto; }
    .s3-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .s5-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .s6-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .s1-inner { padding: 0 36px; }
    .s7-contacts { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .s7-contact { border-right: 1px solid var(--dark3) !important; min-width: 240px; }
    .dots { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="slides">

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 1 — PORTADA ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide active" id="s1">
    <div class="s1-inner">
      <div class="s1-eyebrow">
        <span class="tag">Casa Woden</span>
        <span class="rule"></span>
        <span class="tag">Bahía Blanca</span>
      </div>
      <div class="s1-name">Matías<br>Nicolás<br><em>García</em></div>
      <div class="s1-gold-bar"></div>
      <div class="s1-title">Asesor de imagen masculina · A domicilio</div>
      <div class="s1-contacts">
        <div class="s1-contact">
          <div class="s1-contact-label">WhatsApp</div>
          <div class="s1-contact-value">2916 489044</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s1-contact">
          <div class="s1-contact-label">Instagram</div>
          <div class="s1-contact-value">@casawoden</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s1-contact">
          <div class="s1-contact-label">Disponibilidad</div>
          <div class="s1-contact-value">Todo el año · A domicilio</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 2 — QUIÉN SOY ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide" id="s2">
    <div class="s2-left">
      <span class="tag">Quién soy</span>
      <div class="s2-headline">Asesor de<br><em>imagen</em><br>masculina.</div>
      <div class="s2-body">
        Soy Matías García, fundador de <strong>Casa Woden</strong>. Me especializo en ayudar a hombres profesionales a vestirse bien para su realidad — sin perder tiempo, sin pagar de más, sin complicarse.
        <br><br>
        No soy una tienda. Soy una persona que <strong>selecciona, asesora y lleva la ropa hasta vos.</strong>
